Purpose: Shows the relationship between tables and the technology stack.

System Architecture

Entity Relationship Diagram (ERD)

- Properties (Center): Acts as the bridge between Neighborhoods and Sales.
​
- Sales (Fact Table): Connects Properties to Agents for performance tracking.
​
- Inspections (Sub-table): Linked to Properties via  property_id  for quality analysis.

Tech Stack

- Database: SQL Server / PostgreSQL
​
- Analysis Tools: SQL (CTEs, Window Functions)
​
- Documentation: Markdown
